    <title>WCAG Requirements</title>
    <contents>
      <dl>
        <dt><a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG21/#bypass-blocks" target="_specification">2.4.1 Bypass Blocks</a></dt>
        <dd>A mechanism is available to bypass blocks of content that are repeated on multiple Web pages. (Level A).</dd>
      </dl>
    </contents>
  </slide>

  <slide>
    <title>Traditional Skip links</title>

    <contents>

      <ui>
        <li><a href="https://webedit.disability.illinois.edu/user/jongund/skipto-1/copy/" target="_webedit">Example code for Traditional Skip Link</a></li>
        <li>Use <code>&lt;a href="#main">Skip to main content&lt;/a></code> landmark as target for link.</li>
        <li>Use <code>&lt;main id="main">....&lt;/main></code> landmark as target for link.</li>
        <li>Javascript focus and blur event handlers are used to make the link visible on focus and hidden when it does not have focus.</li>
      </ui>

